title: How to Balance Your Life with Margot Lee

description:
Danielle and her NY roomie Margot Lee catch you up on their time living together and Margot shares her own highlights & lowlights and current faves!

 You can check out our
channels on YouTube:


Brooke Miccio
Danielle Carolan

Link to subscribe to the newsletter: http://bit.ly/2PoNjN6

Instagram and Twitter to be involved in the next episode’s Q&A:
@daniellecarolan @brookemiccio Talk to you guys next Wednesday and for the next
episode!
